          Select distinct
               PROC_DIM_UID
          From     
               PGMPDM.CSTM_DATA_PUBLIC_CNTRY_DIM

               COALESCE(
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_1,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_2,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_3,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_4,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_5,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_6,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_7,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_8,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_9,
                    IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_10,
                    CAST(IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_DATE_1 AS VARCHAR),
                    CAST(IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_DATE_2 AS VARCHAR),
                    CAST(IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_DATE_3 AS VARCHAR),
                    CAST(IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_DATE_4 AS VARCHAR),
                    CAST(IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_DATE_5 AS VARCHAR),
                    CAST(IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_DATE_6 AS VARCHAR),
                    CAST(IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_DATE_7 AS VARCHAR),

                    CAST(IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_DATE_10 AS VARCHAR)
               ) NOT IN ('', 'NULL')

          Select distinct
               DKO.PROC_DIM_UID,
               DKO.IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_1 AS KYNDRYL_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_1,
               DKOTime.UPDATED_TIMESTAMP,
               USER_DIM.CONCAT_NM_LOGIN AS USER_ID -- decrypt_char(USER_DIM.CONCAT_NM_LOGIN, MISC_REP_REF.MIS_REP_REF_CD) AS USER_ID

               PGMPDM.CSTM_DATA_PUBLIC_CNTRY_DIM DKO

                         PROC_ID,
                         IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_1,
                         MIN(UPDATED_TS) AS UPDATED_TIMESTAMP
                    From
                         APPFUN.CSTM_DATA_IBM_CLIENT_CNTRY_H
                    Group By
                         PROC_ID, 
                         IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_1                         
               )DKOTime ON (DKOTime.PROC_ID = DKO.PROC_DIM_UID and DKOTime.IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_1 = DKO.IBM_ONLY_CNTRY_TEXT_1)
               LEFT OUTER JOIN PGMPDM.USER_DIM as USER_DIM ON USER_DIM.USER_ID = (
                    Select distinct DKOUser.UPDATED_USERID

                    Where (DKOUser.PROC_ID = DKOTime.PROC_ID and DKOUser.UPDATED_TS = DKOTime.UPDATED_TIMESTAMP))
               LEFT OUTER JOIN PGMPDM.MISC_REP_REF as MISC_REP_REF ON MISC_REP_REF.MIS_REP_REF_UID = 3
